INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Name   : iptables
Type   : Ansible role

Authors: liv community
License: Simplified BSD License

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BUGS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ENHANCEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Ensure safe defaults if parameter 'iptables_filter_policies' is empty
- Improve support of Docker rules and chains

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FEATURES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Add support for table: 'nat'
- Add support for built-in chains: 'FORWARD', 'PREROUTING', 'POSTROUTING'
- Add support for custom chains
- Add support for built-in targets: 'LOG', 'SNAT', 'DNAT'...
- Add support for module: 'limit'
- Add parameter 'iptables_filter_dependencies'
- Add parameter to define incoming interface (-i, --in-interface)
- Add parameter to define outgoing interface (-o, --out-interface)
- Add parameter to set limits (--limit)
- Add parameter to define log prefix (--log-prefix)
- Add parameter to define log level (--log-level)
- Add dependency to configure sysctl parameters: 'net.ipv4.ip_forward', 'net.ipv6.conf.all.forwarding'
